itunes:title: Is it a sacrifice or an Investment?
itunes:author: The Resonance Network
itunes:subtitle: When you use the word sacrifice, what are we really saying? Most times you think of giving up something, but in the context of success, you can't see it as a sacrifice but more as an investment in your future.
